data.description: The dramatic entrance sets the stage for the exquisite living space that awaits you, in this single story built by Perry Homes offering 3031 sqft of luxury living. A double glass door frames the entry of the bonus room (current study), & across the hall is the mudroom area, 3 car garage access, & a secondary bedroom with ensuite.  Prepare to gasp in delight when you enter the living space, with a wall of windows & views of your beautifully landscaped yard with a brand new pool & spa. It's the dream space, at a cost of $100k, for entertaining & making memories. The luxury continues to the private master suite, boasting 3 windows with views of the tranquil backyard. The master spa-like bath has separate vanities, garden tub, & a glass-enclosed shower. Two additional bedrooms are located at the front of the house. Prosper ISD. In addition to the builder upgrades, spa & pool, the current owners extended the wood-look tile into master bedroom & bonus room & epoxied the garage. Turnkey Home.
